{"tid":1620970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚絕對唔係end game","createTime":"2019-10-04T11:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T14:36:34.000Z","uid":166095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b2acc0f1873986f95e05303c6b1800f01eaae08","tid":1620970,"uid":166095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"希望咁多位手足唔今晚唔好咁博，今晚絕對唔係end game。<br />\n<br />\n其實成個政府上下最怕就係經濟冧，經過左暑假、10.1等旺季成績大家都有目共睹，所以政府先緊急加推蒙面法希望快速平息混亂。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地應該要做嘅係拖長整個運動，拖到去聖誕新年，甚至令到班商家同政府覺得沒完沒了，我地就會見到曙光。<br />\n<br />\n所以希望各位手足勿送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1adca43c2027ae9888994741a2cc97ef5726fe8","tid":1620970,"uid":166095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"1/10 推"},{"pid":"fb7e46605c910599b358d44db29abcf70292e0ef","tid":1620970,"uid":166095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"手足唔好送頭啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}